\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 Implementing the Bridge in a React/Capacitor App\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The workflow for the Pakt app involves registering Party B's device and then signing the NDA hash. The following sequence demonstrates the interaction from the TypeScript layer.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
