\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Generate Key
\f1\b0 : Create a tagged key in the hardware.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Request Signature
\f1\b0 : Send the document hash to the native bridge.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
