\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 Required Configuration and Entitlements\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 For the Capacitor app to successfully use these APIs in the App Store, specific entries must be added to the \cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 Info.plist\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2  and the app's entitlements file. Without these, the app will crash upon calling the biometric APIs.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Face ID Description
\f1\b0 : \cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 NSFaceIDUsageDescription\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2  must be a clear, user-facing string explaining why the app needs Face ID (e.g., "Pakt uses Face ID to securely sign NDAs and verify your identity").\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Keychain Access Groups
\f1\b0 : If sharing keys between apps or extensions.\
\ls2\ilvl0
