\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 App Attest Capability
\f1\b0 : Required for using the \cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 DeviceCheck\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2  framework to get cryptographic evidence.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 Cryptographic Evidence and Legal Enforceability\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 For an NDA to be legally enforceable, the Pakt app must store proof that the specific device owner authenticated at a specific time. A simple "authenticated: true" flag in a database is insufficient, as it could be forged by a malicious backend or a compromised app instance.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 Leveraging App Attest for Device Integrity\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The \cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 DeviceCheck\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2  framework\'92s \cf6 \cb7 \strokec6 App Attest\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2  service provides a mechanism to verify that an app instance is genuine and running on an untampered Apple device. This service produces an "attestation object" that can be stored as evidence.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Attestation Object
\f1\b0 : A CBOR-encoded object containing a public key and a certificate chain rooted in Apple\'92s root CA.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Verification
\f1\b0 : The server verifies the attestation to ensure the public key was generated in the Secure Enclave of a real iPhone.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Assertion
\f1\b0 : For every signature (signing an NDA), the app generates an "assertion object" using the attested key. This assertion includes a counter value to prevent replay attacks.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 Data Clusters for the Evidence Chain\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

